      How to measure page loading time with Performance API
    &lt;/h2&gt;
    &lt;small&gt;by Silvestar Bistrović&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.silvestar.codes/articles/how-to-measure-page-loading-time-with-performance-api/&#34;&gt;https://www.silvestar.codes/articles/how-to-measure-page-loading-time-with-performance-api/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/small&gt;
